creator: Blueye Robotics AS
descriptionHtml:
The Blueye app lets you control your Pioneer underwater drone from your Android. You can either use the touch interface to control the drone, or you can connect a wireless game controller.

The app shows telemetry data from the drone such as depth, heading, orientation, water temperature, and battery level, as well as a full HD 1080p/30fps video stream.
descriptionShort: Control your Blueye Pioneer Underwater Drone form your Android device.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Support for new languages: Norwegian, German, and Spanish.
- Add functionality to toggle camera stabilization on/off for Blueye Pro drones by pressing the Mofidier+Y button.
- The app now includes pictures and videos downloaded from the drone in the dive log page.
- Share the complete dive log as a CSV file from the dive log page.
- Generate and export a report as a PDF or Word file from the dive log page.
- Create and import your custom report template under app settings.
